The paper describes a Matlab toolbox for data mining and classification, with a focus on medical and technical problems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and data analysis, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DM (Data Mining). Additionally, the use of wavelet and signal processing toolboxes suggests a possible connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
